---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { site } from "../data/site";
---
<BaseLayout title="Cake Collection and Delivery in Haywards Heath" description="Collection from Haywards Heath and delivery enquiries for made-to-order cakes across nearby West Sussex areas.">
  <section class="section section--blush"><div class="container"><p class="eyebrow">Collection and delivery</p><h1>Made in Haywards Heath</h1><p class="lead">Collection is based in Haywards Heath. Delivery may be available depending on the cake, event date and postcode, and must be confirmed before booking.</p><div class="actions"><a class="button" href="/order/">Check your postcode and date</a><a class="button button--secondary" href={site.whatsapp("Hello GyulRose Cakes, can you confirm whether delivery is available to postcode: ")} target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Ask about delivery</a></div></div></section>
  <section class="section section--white"><div class="container grid grid--3"><article class="card card__body"><h2>Collection</h2><p>Collection details and the agreed time are provided after an order is confirmed. Do not travel before receiving confirmation.</p></article><article class="card card__body"><h2>Local delivery</h2><p>Provide the complete postcode in the quote request. Availability and any delivery cost depend on distance, timing and safe cake transport.</p></article><article class="card card__body"><h2>Event setup</h2><p>Large, tiered or venue cakes may need different transport or setup arrangements. Explain the venue and access requirements when enquiring.</p></article></div></section>
  <section class="section"><div class="container prose"><h2>Before confirming delivery</h2><ul><li>Provide an accurate postcode and event date.</li><li>Explain whether someone can receive the cake within an agreed window.</li><li>Share access, parking, stairs and venue restrictions for larger cakes.</li><li>Keep the cake transport and storage instructions provided with the order.</li></ul><p>This page intentionally does not promise named towns or a fixed radius until the client confirms the real service area.</p></div></section>
</BaseLayout>
